cerbase season|56711|2018|accessdate=10 February 2019}}</ref> |Premier League |19||0||2||0||3||0||colspan=2|—||24||0 |- !colspan=2|Total !86!!3!!11!!0!!10!!0!!4!!0!!111!!3 |- !colspan=3|Career total !214!!7!!17!!0!!10!!0!!9!!0!!250!!7 |}
