==Honours== '''Individual''' *[[West Ham United F.C.|West Ham United]] Young Player of the Year: [[2016–17 West Ham United F.C. season|2016–17]],<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.whufc.com/news/articles/2017/may/09-may/antonio-crowned-betway-hammer-year |title=Antonio crowned Betway Hammer of the Year |publisher=West Ham United F.C. |accessdate=24 May 2017}}</ref> [[2017–18 West Ham United F.C. season|2017–18]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.whufc.com/news/articles/2018/april/25-april/arnautovic-crowned-betway-hammer-year |title=Arnautovic crowned Betway Hammer of the Year |publisher=West Ham United F.C. |accessdate=25 April 2018}}</ref> *[[Republic of Ireland national under-17 football team|Republic of Ireland U17]] Player of the Year: 2017<ref name="3fai2" /> *[[Republic of Ireland national under-19 football team|Republic of Ireland U19]] Player of the Year: 2018<ref name="3fai2"/> *[[Republic of Ireland national football team|Republic of Ireland]] Young Player of the Year: 2019<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/12342/11663263/declan-rice-named-fa-irelands-young-player-of-the-year |title=Declan Rice named FA Ireland's Young Player of the Year |publisher=Sky Sports |accessdate=12 March 2019}}</ref> *London Football Awards Young Player of the Year: 2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://londonfootballawards.org/|title=The London Football Awards 2019 – Celebrating the very best of London Football|website=londonfootballawards.org|access-date=2019-03-01}}</ref> *[[FAI Young International Player of the Year|Irish Young Player of the Year]] 2019<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/47542669|title=Declan Rice wins Irish Young Player of the Year award despite declaring for England|date=12 March 2019|publisher=|via=www.bbc.co.uk}}</ref>
